high_descs: Walk to the dresser on the left.
Pick up the round bottle on the dresser.
Move away from the dresser.
Put the bottle in the second drawer of the dresser.
Turn around, walk to the white shelves.
Pick up the round bottle on the end of the shelf.
Turn around, walk back to the dresser.
Place the bottle in the second drawer of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put two round bottles in the dresser.

high_descs: Move to the dresser to the left of the door
pick up a dispenser from the dresser
move to the dresser ahead of you
put the dispenser in the drawer second from the top
move to the counter behind you
pick up a dispenser from the counter
Move to the dresser to the left of the door
put the dispenser in the drawer second from the top
anns.task_desc: Put two dispensers in the drawer second from the top in the dresser.

high_descs: Turn left to face the dresser.
Pick up the lotion bottle.
Step back from the dresser.
Open the second drawer from the top and put the lotion inside.
Turn around to face the shelves.
Pick up the lotion bottle from the shelf.
Turn around and face the dresser again.
Put the lotion in the same drawer as the first bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put two lotion bottles in the dresser.
